K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-10: tu phyin pa 'di med par mi 'gyur bar gyis
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-12: ji srid du shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-13: pa 'di 'jig rten na gnas pa de srid du
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-14: de bzhin gshegs pa'ang bzhugs par rig par bya; de
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-15: srid du de bzhin gshegs pa chos 'chad par rig
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-17: sems can gang dag shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyan pa dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-21: kun chub par byed pa dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-28: bsti stang du byed pa dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-42: kho ra khor yug tu mar me'i phreng ba rnam
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-43: pa sna tshogs kyi mchod pas mchod par byed pa'i
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:536b-44: sems can de dag ni sangs rgyas mthong ba dang
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-1: chos nyan pa dang mi 'bral bar rig par bya'o //
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-3: sems can de dag ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i zham ring bar 'khod par rig par bya'o //
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-4: bcom ldan 'das thugs dgyes pas de skad ces bka' stsal pa dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-5: tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-6: tshe dang ldan pa sh'a ri'i bu dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-7: tshe dang ldan pa moonggal chen po'i bu dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-8: tshe dang ldan pa 'od srung chen po dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-9: tshe dang ldan pa byams ma'i bu gang po dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-10: tshe dang ldan pa ka ta ya na chen po dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-11: tshe dang ldan pa ma 'gags pa dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-12: tshe dang ldan pa re ba ta dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-13: tshe dang ldan pa r'a hu la dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-17: lha ma yin du bcas pa'i 'jig rten pa bcom
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-18: ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa la mngon par dga'
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-19: bar gyur to; ;shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-20: pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa las /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-21: yongs su gtad pa'i le'u ste bdun cu rtsa drug pa'o ////
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-22: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-23: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi 'das pa dang /
K03D0009-3_H0010-3:537a-25: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas dang /
